Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Output gifs/zap-send.gif

Hide
Type "export PS1='darren@ForgeSworn.dev:bray $ '"
Enter
Type "alias claude=/Users/darren/WebstormProjects/bray/site/demos/bray-demo.sh"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "claude -p 'Switch to the demo persona, check the wallet balance, then create a lightning invoice for 21 sats'"
Enter
Sleep 25s
